---
title: Tandoori Chicken & Cauliflower Traybake with Mint Yoghurt
description: Traybakes are the superstars of no-fuss dinners. For this delicious dish, all you need to do is throw tandoori chicken and a solid array of veggies on a tray in the oven. Too easy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tandoori-chicken-cauliflower-tray-bake-b2d1f0c1.jpg
